# API Generated Client Rules

- Use generated services from `src/app/api/api/` for API calls.
- Use generated types from `src/app/api/model/models`.
- Do not edit generated files under `src/app/api/`; regenerate instead.
- Wrap generated services inside feature services for feature-specific behavior.
- Avoid direct `HttpClient` endpoint calls unless explicitly required as a temporary workaround.
- If fetch-mode Blob responses apply, handle Blob-to-JSON conversion in wrapper services.

## Example

- ✅ `private itemsService = inject(ItemsService);`
- ❌ `return this.http.get('/api/items')`
